# Music Directory

Place background music files here:
- background.mp3 - Main game background music
- menu.mp3 - Menu/title screen music
- battle.mp3 - Battle/action music

## Recommended Specifications:
- Format: MP3 (best compatibility)
- Quality: 128-192 kbps
- Length: 2-5 minutes (will loop automatically)
- Volume: Normalized to -6dB to prevent clipping